Class ChartGraph

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.application.Application
      • view.ChartGraph

  • public class ChartGraph
extends javafx.application.Application
    Instantiates an JavaFX application which creates a model of the data. Uses the model to instantiate an object of type javafx.scene.chart.LineChart via the GraphView class. Then sets up the scene with basic modification to the stage.
    Author:
    Foothill College, Zerong Li (Jerry), Qianli Li
